Class BulkProduct

java.lang.Object
  edu.uci.inf111.SelfCheckOut.App.BulkProduct
All Implemented Interfaces:
ProductInfo
public class BulkProduct
extends java.lang.Object
implements ProductInfo

The BulkProduct class represents a grocery product which is sold by weight, such as produce, deli, meat, etc. The details of the product are stored at the time of construction, and can be retrieved using accessor functions.
